@startuml SD_08_QRCheckIn
' ============================================================
' SEQUENCE DIAGRAM - Check-in QR Code
' FR-26~FR-28: Scan QR → Validate → Confirm Check-in
' ============================================================

title **SD-08: Check-in QR Code\n(QR Scan → Validate → Confirm)**

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #F3E5F5
    ParticipantBorderColor #7B1FA2
    ArrowColor #7B1FA2
}

actor "Staff/Organizer" as Staff #LightCoral
participant "Browser\n(Mobile)" as Browser #LightYellow
participant "CheckInServlet\n(Controller)" as Controller #F3E5F5
participant "CheckInService" as Service #E8F5E9
participant "TicketDAO" as TicketDAO #FFF3E0
participant "OrderDAO" as OrderDAO #FFF3E0
database "SQL Server" as DB #F3E5F5

== Bước 1: Mở trang Check-in ==

Staff -> Browser: Truy cập trang Check-in
Browser -> Controller: GET /organizer/checkin?eventId={id}\n(hoặc /staff/checkin?eventId={id})
activate Controller
Controller -> Controller: Validate:\nuser có quyền check-in\ncho event này?
Controller -> DB: SELECT event info +\ncheckin stats
activate DB
DB --> Controller: Event + stats:\n{total: 500, checkedIn: 123}
deactivate DB
Controller --> Browser: Forward → checkin.jsp\n(event info, camera controls,\nmanual input, stats)
deactivate Controller
Browser --> User: Hiển thị trang Check-in:\n- Camera QR scanner (jsQR)\n- Input thủ công\n- Stats: 123/500 đã check-in

== Bước 2: Scan QR Code ==

Staff -> Browser: Hướng camera vào\nQR code trên vé
Browser -> Browser: jsQR library:\nDecode QR → Extract data\n(JWT token hoặc ticketCode)

alt QR chứa JWT Token
    Browser -> Browser: Extract ticketCode\nfrom JWT payload\n(client-side decode)
end

Browser -> Controller: POST /api/checkin\n{ticketCode: "TKT-A1B2C3D4",\neventId: 123}
activate Controller

== Bước 3: Server Validation ==

Controller -> Service: processCheckIn(\nticketCode, eventId, staffId)
activate Service

' --- Step 1: Find Ticket ---
Service -> TicketDAO: findByTicketCode(ticketCode)
activate TicketDAO
TicketDAO -> DB: SELECT t.*, tt.name as typeName,\no.status as orderStatus,\no.buyerName, o.buyerEmail,\ne.eventId as ticketEventId\nFROM Tickets t\nJOIN OrderItems oi ON t.orderItemId = oi.orderItemId\nJOIN TicketTypes tt ON oi.ticketTypeId = tt.ticketTypeId\nJOIN Orders o ON t.orderId = o.orderId\nJOIN Events e ON o.eventId = e.eventId\nWHERE t.ticketCode = ?
activate DB
DB --> TicketDAO: Ticket + Order + Event data
deactivate DB
TicketDAO --> Service: TicketInfo or null
deactivate TicketDAO

' --- Validation Chain ---
alt #FFE0E0 Ticket NOT found
    Service --> Controller: CheckInResult\n{success: false,\nmessage: "❌ Vé không hợp lệ.\nMã vé không tồn tại\ntrong hệ thống."}

else #FFFDE7 Order NOT confirmed
    Service -> Service: Check: order.status\n== "confirmed"?
    Service --> Controller: CheckInResult\n{success: false,\nmessage: "❌ Đơn hàng chưa\nthanh toán (status: pending)"}

else #FFFDE7 Wrong Event
    Service -> Service: Check: ticket.eventId\n== requested eventId?
    Service --> Controller: CheckInResult\n{success: false,\nmessage: "❌ Vé không thuộc\nsự kiện này"}

else #FFFDE7 Already Checked In
    Service -> Service: Check: ticket.isCheckedIn\n== false?
    Service --> Controller: CheckInResult\n{success: false,\nmessage: "⚠️ Vé đã được check-in\nlúc {checkedInAt}\nbởi {checkedInBy}"}

else #E8F5E9 All Validations Passed

    == Bước 4: Mark Check-in ==

    Service -> TicketDAO: markCheckedIn(\nticketId, staffId)
    activate TicketDAO
    TicketDAO -> DB: UPDATE Tickets SET\nisCheckedIn = 1,\ncheckedInAt = GETDATE(),\ncheckedInBy = ?\nWHERE ticketId = ?
    activate DB
    DB --> TicketDAO: Updated
    deactivate DB
    TicketDAO --> Service: OK
    deactivate TicketDAO

    Service --> Controller: CheckInResult\n{success: true,\nmessage: "✅ Check-in thành công!",\nattendee: {\n  name: "Nguyễn Văn A",\n  ticketType: "VIP",\n  ticketCode: "TKT-A1B2C3D4"\n}}
end

deactivate Service

Controller --> Browser: JSON Response\n{success, message, attendee}
deactivate Controller

== Bước 5: Hiển thị kết quả ==

alt success == true
    Browser -> Browser: ✅ Animation + Sound\nHiển thị thông tin attendee:\n- Tên: Nguyễn Văn A\n- Loại vé: VIP\n- Mã: TKT-A1B2C3D4
    Browser -> Browser: Update stats:\ncheckedIn: 124/500 (24.8%)
    Browser --> Staff: ✅ Check-in thành công

else success == false
    Browser -> Browser: ❌ Error animation\nHiển thị message lỗi\n(đỏ hoặc vàng tùy loại)
    Browser --> Staff: ❌ / ⚠️ Thông báo lỗi
end

note over Browser
  Sau 3 giây tự động reset
  camera để sẵn sàng scan tiếp
end note

== Alternative: Nhập mã thủ công ==

Staff -> Browser: Nhập mã vé "TKT-A1B2C3D4"
Browser -> Controller: POST /api/checkin\n{ticketCode: "TKT-A1B2C3D4",\neventId: 123}
note over Browser, Controller
  Cùng luồng xử lý như QR scan
end note

@enduml
